com.quest.glue.api.services
Interface WMIObject

All Superinterfaces:
java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object>
public interface WMIObject
extends java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object>

An object made up of name/value pairs. Objects can be returned through queries and can contain other objects, strings, numbers, and references as their properties.

For convenience, WMIObjects implement the Map interface but access is currently read-only.

Since:
5.5.5.3
